{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"1036","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"缺工讓全球糧食供應鏈拉警報 食品價格漲勢難擋","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>2021-09-02 14:46 經濟日報 編譯黃淑玲/綜合外電</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>彭博資訊報導，因為工人短缺，全球食物供應鏈現在拉警報。越南必須派出軍隊幫忙稻田收割，英國酪農被迫倒掉牛奶，因為沒有卡車司機能開車過來運走。巴西的羅布斯塔咖啡豆今年花120天才能收成完畢，而非往年90天就能解決。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>一家美國肉品處理商招募員工，需要用贈送蘋果智慧手表的福利來吸引人前來。速食連鎖店因為各種成本大增，調高了漢堡和捲餅的價格。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>全球食品業生態系裡，到處缺工。沒足夠的工人採收水果、屠宰、開貨運卡車，倉儲找不到操作員，餐聽聘不到廚師和服務生。食物供應量能因而受到衝擊。部分雇主必須以兩位數的加薪幅度找來或留住員工。而食物的價格已經因為原物料和海運成本高漲面臨漲價壓力，人力成本再往上加，只會漲得更凶。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>彭博說，聯合國糧農組織（FAO）彙編的指數顯示，7月食物價格較去年同期年上漲31%。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>波士頓諮詢公司表示，新冠疫情讓經濟活動中多個環節的人力供應面臨短缺，但對食物和農業領域的衝擊最大。因為農糧業是全球自動化程度最低的產業。然而食物供應安全又是高度敏感課題，加以這領域本就利潤偏低，成本一提升，就基本上都轉嫁給買方。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>勞工短缺令供應吃緊的現象最近已頻頻出現，美國的食品製造批發商Sysco和United Natural Foods最近傳出生產延誤，從燻肉到起司到椰子水等產品都受到影響。英國一些店家欠缺麵包、雞肉。麥當勞上個月奶昔缺貨停賣。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><img alt='' src='http://www.ctspcsr.com.tw/user_files/news_files/%E7%B3%A7%E9%A3%9F0903.JPG' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 100%;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'>資料來源：</span><a href='https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/5717518' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 158, 184); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px !important;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/5717518</span></a></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2021-09-03","clk_count":"137"}},"__N_SSG":true}